Beat up nine Mandalorian Rangers and return to Orlando Doon for your reward.
You beat up nine Mandalorian Rangers. Return to Orlando Doon in Veles Colony for your reward.
Blast the Mandalorian Rangers

Denam Reyholm has instructed you to locate someone in Veles Colony. He doesn't know the person's real name or what he looks like. All he could tell you is that he goes by "L" and he's somewhere in the colony. Speak to him and speak the code phrases.
You located "L", gave the appropriate pass phrases and he gave you an old tome. Return the tome to Denam Reyholm and let him know what happened.
Coxxion Initiation

The Crafting Terminal Droid operator has requested you create a single unit of Fiberplast Padding. You can use any armorsmith terminal to make the item. You will find the necessary resources down on the maintenance level.
Talk to the Crafting Terminal Droid operator for your reward.
CZ-220 Supplies - Armorsmith

The Crafting Terminal Droid operator has requested you create a Basic Resource Scanner. You can use any engineering terminal to make the item. You will find the necessary resources down on the maintenance level.
Speak to the Crafting Terminal Droid operator for your reward.
CZ-220 Supplies - Engineering

The Crafting Terminal Droid operator has requested you create a single unit of Power Core. You can use any fabrication terminal to make the item. You will find the necessary resources down on the maintenance level.
Speak to the Crafting Terminal Droid operator for your reward.
CZ-220 Supplies - Fabrication

The Crafting Terminal Droid operator has requested you gather ten units of scrap metal. You will need to scavenge through junk piles throughout the facility. When you have enough, return to the droid to collect your receipt.
Speak to the Crafting Terminal Droid operator for your reward.
CZ-220 Supplies - Scavenging

The Crafting Terminal Droid operator has requested you create a single unit of Basic Baton C. You will need to purchase the "Weaponsmith Blueprints" perk in order to create this item. Once you have the perk you can use any weaponsmith terminal to make the item. You will find the necessary resources down on the maintenance level.
Speak to the Crafting Terminal Droid operator for your reward.
CZ-220 Supplies - Weaponsmith
Crystal in Veles Colony needs five units of Basic Finesse Vibroblade D. Collect them and return them to her.
You delivered five units of Basic Finesse Vibroblade D to Crystal. Talk to her for your reward.
Daggers for Crystal

You're responsible for culling back the Kath Hound population in the Viscara Wildlands. Slay 7 of them and return to Moira Halaz in the Veles Colony for your reward.

Kath Hound Hunting
Szaan in Veles Colony needs five units of Kath Hound Teeth and five units of Kath Hound Fur. Return to him with these items to collect your reward.
Speak to Szaan in Veles Colony to retrieve your reward.
Kath Hound Part Collection
There are reports of a Mandalorian facility located somewhere in the Wildwoods. Search the woods, find the facility, and report back to Tal'gar in Veles Colony.
You found the Mandalorian facility but it's locked. Return to Tal'gar and report your findings.
Locate the Mandalorian Facility
Defeat Mandalorian raiders and return five of their dog tags to Irene Colsstaad in Veles Colony.
Speak to Irene Colsstaad for your reward.
Mandalorian Dog Tags

Halron Linth wants you to head down to the maintenance level and kill some unwanted Mynocks. Cull back their numbers, obtain their teeth and return to him for your receipt. He has requested five of them.
You've killed five Mynocks and obtained their teeth. Return to Halron Linth to collect your work receipt.
Mynock Mayhem
Avix Tatham needs you to head down to the maintenance level and harvest some ore. When you have ten pieces, return to him to collect the work receipt.
Speak to Avix Tatham for your reward.
Ore Collection

Avix Tatham wants you to go down and gather more ore. This time, though, he needs you to refine it at one of the refineries near him. When you have ten pieces of refined Veldite return to him to give them to him.
Speak to Avix Tatham for your reward.
Refinery Trainee

Farah Oersted needs you to collect the following items: Light Armor Repair Kit I, Blaster Rifle Repair Kit I, and Blaster Pistol Repair Kit I. These can be created at the appropriate crafting workbench. Gather them and give them to her for your reward.
Repairing Coxxion Equipment

Selan Flembek, receptionist at CZ-220, has requested you complete three tasks around the base. 

Speak to Avix Tatham, the mining coordinator, for information about retrieving ore from the mine.

Talk to security officer Harlon Linth for information about trouble on the maintenance level.

Chat with the Crafting Terminal Droid Operator for details about supplies which need to be constructed.

When you've obtained receipts from all three employees, return to Selan to collect your reward.
Selan's Request
Harry Mason needs you to slice six terminals found in the Mandalorian Facility. Obtain the data from each of the terminals and return them to him.
Slicing the Mandalorian Facility
Roy Moss gave you a less-than-legal package to deliver to Denam Reyholm. He can be found out in the mountain region of Viscara, near an old refinery.
Smuggle Roy Moss's Package

Farah Oersted needs you to collect the following items: Finesse Vibroblade Repair Kit I, Heavy Vibroblade Repair Kit I, and Polearm Repair Kit I. These can be created at the appropriate crafting workbench. Gather them and give them to her for your reward.
Stuff Keeps Breaking!

Halron Linth has one final mission for you. He wants you to head back down to the maintenance level of CZ-220 and locate the experimental Colicoid locked in one of the rooms. You should prepare thoroughly as it will be a tough fight!
You made quick work of the rampaging Colicoid experiment. Return to Halron Linth to let him know the work is done.
The Colicoid Experiment
Halron Linth wants you to head back down to the maintenance level and take care of a few malfunctioning droids.
You've destroyed five malfunctioning droids. Return to Halron Linth for your reward.
The Malfunctioning Droids
Tal'gar wants you to avenge Captain N'guth's death. Enter the Mandalorian facility, kill the War Hero, and report back to him when it's done.
You found and killed the Mandalorian War Hero. Return to Tal'gar to report.
The Mandalorian War Hero
Infiltrate the Coxxion base and drive the raiders out of it. Return to Reid Coxxion when the work is done.
You defeated the Coxxion Fleshleader. Return to Reid Coxxion to finish the job.
Vanquish the Vellen Raiders
Beat up nine Mandalorian Warriors and return to Orlando Doon for your reward.
You beat up nine Mandalorian Warriors. Return to Orlando Doon in Veles Colony for your reward.
War With the Mandalorian Warriors
